- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper describes the use of a deep learning technique (CNN) for steering the robot.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper describes the use of an AI technique (CNN) for decision making.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper describes the use of a neural network (CNN) for decision making.
